title: Derek and the Dominos
description:
Ever heard of Eric Clapton?  Can you name his first band?  If you said Blind Faith you are correct!  Well, okay.  Have you ever heard of Duane Allman? If you knew, Duane was the studio musician for a long time. As the anthology set shows, Duane did slide with a lot of famous people on a lot of famous stuff!  For one, Layla which was originaly done by Clapton&#039;s 2nd band. Derek and the Dominoes... This then is that: If you want me to upload the Duane Allman Anthology (2 CD set) let me know. Also, if you&#039;ve got ANY requests for specific artists or albums hit me up, I just might have it. I&#039;ve got 110 gigabytes of tunage and more all the time.

I got some Anderson, Bruford, Wakeman and Howe youd probably like!  (YES)
